column1: Agency for Education of the Poor Rural Youth (AEPRY)
column2:
Our Strategic Vision


AEPRY envisions itself as an instrument for the holistic development of the poor families in rural and urban areas through rendering good education to the new generations and implementing rural development.


Our Mission Statements


AEPRY firmly stands as a government recognized Educational Organization for the healthy development of the poor families both from rural and urban areas in Myanmar through:


Enhancing the capacity of human resources

Supporting children to be able to seek higher education

Providing vocational skills to school drop outs

Improving families’ financial situation

Building a healthy atmosphere to the poor families

Generating highly educated citizens among the poor families

Building a society influenced by well educated young people
